  "detailed_description": "Maze Shooter is more special, after the player enters the maze, you need to think and observe calmly, and we have given the player a very open idea in the design of the maze, there can be many ways to pass through the maze, and inexplicable assassin-type monsters will suddenly appear in the maze, defeat them, go to the central tower, where a very interesting creature is waiting for you. Grab your medal of wisdom.<br />\r\nBy the way, in the spaceship where the player is, there is a little game hidden, go and find out.",
  "about_the_game": "Maze Shooter is more special, after the player enters the maze, you need to think and observe calmly, and we have given the player a very open idea in the design of the maze, there can be many ways to pass through the maze, and inexplicable assassin-type monsters will suddenly appear in the maze, defeat them, go to the central tower, where a very interesting creature is waiting for you. Grab your medal of wisdom.<br />\r\nBy the way, in the spaceship where the player is, there is a little game hidden, go and find out.",
